    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, r u sure? i've had cramps like this before and they usually just go away with ibuprofen. can't i just try the aspirin and ibuprofen thing first to see if it calms down? i really dont want to go to the er if i can help it, it's so expensive and i have work tomorrow morning.",
