      "content": "okay okay i get it. it just sounds so extreme. i'm kind of scared. if i can't take the painkillers, what else can i do? is there like a heating pad i can use or maybe some tea to help with the inflammation? i just really need some way to manage the discomfort until i can potentially see someone tomorrow.",
